    + `sources` : `political,maritime` (string, optional) - Comma separated list of Sources. For Verfied Events sources must be 'political,maritime'.
   
    + `eventType`: `verified` (string, optional) - Verified Event Type. [verified]
    
    + `pageSize`: 5  (number, optional) - The number of results per page.
    
        
    

