## PulseCityPropertiesType (object)
+ `id`: `et-001` (string) - identifier for the location.  For Pulse Cities this is the same as `cityCode`.
+ `country` : et (string) - ISO-3166-1 Alpha 2 Country Code associated with the results
+ `city` : Addis Ababa (string) - Name of the city for the Pulse Values
+ `cityCode` : `et-001` (string) - City Code, these are unique to Seerist and are ISO-3166-1 Alpha 2 Country Codes + an index (001)
+ `stability_score` (StabilityScoreCountryType)
+ `startTime`: `2019-04-10T00:00:00.000Z` - Date of the Pulse value
+ `subscores` (string) - IGNORE
+ `forecast` (array[ForecastType])

## PulseCountyPropertiesType (object)'
+ `id`: `us-fips-51107` (string) - identifier for the location.  For Pulse Counties this is the same as `fipsCode`.
+ `country` : us (string) - ISO-3166-1 Alpha 2 Country Code associated with the results
+ `county` : Loudoun (string) - Name of the county for the Pulse Values
+ `state` : va (string) - 2 letter US state abbreviation
+ `fipsCode` : `us-fips-51107` (string) - FIPS Code, "us-fips-" + US FIPS code
+ `stability_score` (StabilityScoreCountryType)
+ `startTime`: `2019-04-10T00:00:00.000Z` - Date of the Pulse value
+ `subscores` (string) - IGNORE
+ `forecast` (array[ForecastType])

