+ `features` (array[FeatureCollectionPulseCountryCodeType])

## MetadataPulseCountryCodeType (object)
+ `status` : success (string) - This will indicate if the call was successful or a failure
+ `statusCode` : 200 (number) - HTTP Status code of the response
+ `count` : 1 (number) - Count of results in the Features array
+ `total` : 1 (number) - Total number of results produced by the query, all can be retrieved via paging
+ `startDate` : 2019-01-22T00:00:00.000Z (string) - Start Date of the Pulse Scores
+ `endDate` : 2019-01-22T23:59:59.999Z (string) - End Date of the Pulse Scores
+ `prev` : url (string) - A url to the previous set of results, null if no prior results exist
+ `next` : url (string) - A url to the next set of results, null if no next results exist
+ `daily_histogram` : ignore (string) - Ignore this it will be removed in future deployments
+ `global_histogram` : ignore (string) - Ignore this it will be removed in future deployments
+ `country` : us (string) - Country Code for this response, these are ISO-3166-1 Alpha 2 Country Codes
+ `forecast` (array[ForecastType])
+ `stats` (StatsType)

