## MetadataEventsCodeType (object)
+ `status`: success (string) - This will indicate if the call was successful or a failure
+ `statusCode`: 200 (number) - HTTP Status code of the response
+ `pageSize`: 10 (number) - Max Results to return 
+ `prev`: url (string) - A url to the previous set of results, null if no prior results exist
+ `next`: url (string) - A url to the next set of results, null if no next results exist
+ `totalsFiltered` (EventsTotalsFilteredType) - Total number of events with applied topic filters
+ `totalsOverall` (EventsTotalsType) - Total number of Events without any filters applied

## MetadataWodCodeType (object)
+ `status`: success (string) - This will indicate if the call was successful or a failure
+ `statusCode`: 200 (number) - HTTP Status code of the response
+ `pageSize`: 10 (number) - Max Results to return 
+ `prev`: url (string) - A url to the previous set of results, null if no prior results exist
+ `next`: url (string) - A url to the next set of results, null if no next results exist
+ `total`:15 (number) - Total number of matching documents
+ `filterCounts` (FilterCountsType) - The number of documents that match a particular filter if it were to be enabled (enabled via the includeFilterCounts query string parameter)

## MetadataWodBaseCodeType (object)
+ `status`: success (string) - This will indicate if the call was successful or a failure
+ `statusCode`: 200 (number) - HTTP Status code of the response
+ `pageSize`: 10 (number) - Max Results to return
+ `prev`: url (string) - A url to the previous set of results, null if no prior results exist
+ `next`: url (string) - A url to the next set of results, null if no next results exist
+ `total`:1 (number) - Total number of matching documents

