## EventsType (object)
+ `id`: `e0f5a05c1d4642bd87ca3999f4d7e771` (string) - Unique Identifier for the Article chosen to represent the cluster, this can change as the cluster evolves
+ `cluster_id`: `46f21da9-3fac-435d-a3de-e97f7a416c00` (string) - GUID for the Cluster, this will not change as the cluster evolves
+ `cluster_size`: 8 (number, optional) - Number of articles in this cluster
+ `updated`: `2020-10-07T18:45:56.105Z` (string) - Time when the most recent article was added to the cluster
+ `timestamp`: `2020-10-07T18:45:56.105Z` (string) - Publish date of the Article chosen to represent the cluster
+ `title`: `article title` (string) - Title of the Article chosen to represent the cluster
+ `summary`: `article summary` (string) - Short Summary of the Article chosen to represent the cluster
+ `lang`: en (string, optional) - Language code (ISO-639-1) for the Article Source
+ `translated`: true (boolean, optional) - True if the Summary and/Or Title were translated TO English from 'lang'
+ `veracity`: `Official Source` (string) - Our determination of the quality of the original Source, for a definition of each see here: https://seerist.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/BGS/pages/1563459585/Article+Veracity
+ `source_url`: `http://url.to/original/article` (string) - A web URL to the original source of the Article
+ `image_url`: `http://url.to/image/associated/with/article.png` (string, optional) - A web URL to an image that was associated with the Article
+ `topic_scores` (EventTopicScoresType) - Dynamic list of the topic scores the articles in the cluster, for more information see here: https://seerist.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/BGS/pages/1562804251/Event+Clusters
+ `category_types` (array[string]) - Topic Category's this cluster matched to, this list is dynamic and will change over time
+ `source`: `domain.com` - Domain Name for this Article
+ `location_metadata` (LocationMetadata)
+ `severity`: 6 (number, optional) - Severity of the article (0 - 10)

