## SavedSearchParamsType
+ `search`: `some keywords` (string, optional) - text to search
+ `start`: `2019-01-22T00:00:00.000Z` (string, optional) - Start of the date (and optionally time), e.g. 2016-09-15T00:00:00.000
+ `end`: `2019-01-22T00:00:00.000Z` (string, optional) - Start of the date (and optionally time), e.g. 2016-09-15T00:00:00.000
+ `time_range`: `-7` (number, optional) - Number of days for search to look back. (Incompatible with start and end)
+ `bounds`: `-85.0511,-180.0000,82.1866,79.5153` (string, optional) - Geospatial Bounding Box to restrict the search to.
+ `bounds_type` (SavedSearchBoundsType, optional) - Determines how bounds will be treated
+ `sources` (array[LiveSearchSources], optional) - List of Sources for search to use
+ `topics`: `crime` (array[string]) - Topics for search to use.
+ `places` (array[SavedSearchParamsPlacesType], optional) - List of places

