## MetadataEventArticlesCodeType (object)
+ `status`: success (string) - This will indicate if the call was successful or a failure
+ `statusCode`: 200 (number) - HTTP Status code of the response
+ `total`: 9 (number) - Number of results in this response, if count > total use the next link to get the next set of results
+ `count`: 9 (number) - Total number of results produced by the query, all can be retrieved via paging
+ `prev`: url (string) - A url to the previous set of results, null if no prior results exist
+ `next`: url (string) - A url to the next set of results, null if no next results exist
+ `pageSize`: 10 (number) - Max Results to return

## FeatureCollectionEventArticlesType (object)
+ `type`: Feature (fixed) - Will be 'Feature'
+ `properties` (EventArticlesType)
+ `geometry` (Geometry)

## EventArticlesType (object)
+ `id`: `1509a9ef51895eb61c182dd20ac59038` (string) - unique Article Identifier
+ `cluster_id`: `46f21da9-3fac-435d-a3de-e97f7a416c00` (string, optional) - GUID for the Cluster
+ `timestamp`: `2020-10-07T14:15:00.000Z` (string) - Article Publish Date, if we are unable to extract an Article Publish Date this will be the time of ingest into our platform
+ `title`: `Article Title` (string) - Title of the article
+ `summary`: `article summary` (string) - Short Summary of the article in it's original language
+ `lang`: en (string, optional) - Language code (ISO-639-1) for the Article Source
+ `translated`: true (boolean, optional) - True if the Summary and/Or Title were translated TO English from 'lang'
+ `veracity`: `Official Source` (string) - Our determination of the quality of the original Source, for a definition of each see here: https://seerist.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/BGS/pages/1563459585/Article+Veracity
+ `source_url`: `http://url.to/original/article` (string) - A web URL to the original source of the Article
+ `image_url`: `http://url.to/image/associated/with/article.png` (string, optional) - A web URL to an image that was associated with the Article
+ `topic_scores` (EventTopicScoresType) - Dynamic list of the topic scores the article matched, for more information see here: https://seerist.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/BGS/pages/1562804251/Event+Clusters
+ `category_types` (array[string]) - Topic Category's this article matched to
+ `source`: `domain.com` - Domain Name for this Article
+ `location_metadata` (LocationMetadata)
+ `severity`: 6 (number, optional) - Severity of the article (0 - 10)

