## TopicScoresV2 (object)
+ `score`: 0.86463 (number) - Confidence Score for this Article that it fits the particular topic, Articles with a score > 0.8 are considered a match
+ `name`: `health` (string) - Name of the topic to which the score corresponds

## TopicScoresV2More (object)
+ `score`: 0.99 (number) - Confidence Score for this Article that it fits the particular topic, Articles with a score > 0.8 are considered a match
+ `name`: `<more>` (string) - This is a dynamic list and can include 1 or more topic scores

## TopicVersions (object)
+ `health`: `1.4.0` (string) - The current working version of the given model
+ `<more>`: `1.0.0` (string) - This is a dynamic list and can include 1 or more topic score versions

## EntityOrgs (array, fixed)
List of Organizations found in the Article by our Named Entity Recognition processes

### Items
- `THE UNITED NATIONS` (string) - Fully capitalized version of an organization entity extracted from the Article
- `<more>` (string) - This is a dynamic list and can include 0 or more extracted organizations

## EntityFacs (array, fixed)
List of facilities or points of interest found in the Article by our Named Entity Recognition process

### Items
- `THE HENNEPIN COUNTY COURTHOUSE` (string) - Fully capitalized version of a facility entity extracted from the Article
- `<more>` (string) - This is a dynamic list and can include 0 or more extracted facilities

## TopicSubtypeSubcomponents (array, fixed)
List of lowest-level topic subtype subcomponents that apply to this Article

### Items
- `transportation_maritime_port` (string) - Name of a topic subtype subcomponent that this Article has been classified under
- `<more>` (string) - This is a dynamic list and can include 0 or more subtype subcomponents

## EntityLocation (array, fixed)
